n class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p>由于美国经济的资本份额约为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 30 \% "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">30</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">%</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，这大致意味着我们认为总产出与资本存量成<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 0.3 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.3</span></span></span></span></span></span>次方；由于资本被认为是线性积累的，平价假说预测美国全要素生产率<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" r = 0.3 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.3</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。<a href="https://web.stanford.edu/~chadj/IdeaPF.pdf">布鲁姆等人。 （2020）</a>几乎完全验证了这一预测。</p></li><li><p>当我们关注利基问题时，我们必须小心，因为一些效率术语（例如摩尔定律）是由全球投资驱动的，而这些投资并未针对我们的利基应用进行优化。然后，这成为一个外生进展术语，并且最好将内生术语相互比较。</p><p>在机器学习中，计算扩展比摩尔定律快得多，因此我们希望我们的模型在这种情况下能够成为一个很好的近似值。如果我们假设计算支出线性累积，则<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" r_{\text{compute}} = 1 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">rcompute</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">=</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">，</span></span></span></span></span></span>奇偶校验结果表明我们也应该期望<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" r_{\text{software}} \approx 1 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.23em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">rsoftware</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">≈</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span>我有一些未发表的估计支持类似的观点，但公共参考是<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/Gc9FGtdXhK9sCSEYu/what-a-compute-centric-framework-says-about-ai-takeoff">Tom Davidson 的起飞模型</a>，他估计计算机视觉中的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" r \approx 2.5 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">≈</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2.5</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。不完全是<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 1 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，但也相差不远。</p></li></ol><p>我认为玩具模型<em>通常</em>表明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" r_{\text{efficiency}} "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.23em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">效率</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>趋向于<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" O(1) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">O</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。我们没有充分的<em>先验</em>理由来期待这一点，但事实上，情况似乎确实如此。从一个角度来看，这实际上是表达宇称假设的另一种方式，但我认为这可能有助于思考这一现象。</p><p>当然，对于这种“巧合”还有其他可能的解释，但似乎没有一个是完全令人满意的，这令人相当失望。</p><br/><br/> <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/Q3XaZTExzDpCLr4wu/efficiency-and-resource-use-scaling-parity#comments">讨论</a>; https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/Q3XaZTExzDpCLr4wu/efficiency-and-resource-use-scaling-parity Q3XaZTExzDpCLr4wuEge Erdil Mon, 21 Aug 2023 00:18:01 GMT 
