</style>。她会把所有的钱都赌在这场比赛上。如果她赢了，她会再赌一次。如此反复，直到最终她输了，再也没有钱了。</p><p> Logan 的效用函数是货币的对数， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" U_\text{Logan}(m) = \ln(m) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.084em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mtext" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">Logan</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">ln</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">米</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。他每次都会押注20%的资金，他的财富就会成倍增长。</p><p>有些人认为这是成为洛根而不是琳达的理由。为什么要使用一个让你下注最终让你陷入贫困的效用函数，而不是一个让你下注让你变得富有的效用函数呢？</p><h3>为琳达辩护</h3><p>我对此作出三个答复。首先，实用功能不是可以争夺的！每当有人建议改变你对某事物的重视程度时，你都应该非常怀疑。</p><p> “因为如果琳达拥有洛根的效用函数，她会更富有。根据她当前的效用函数，她会做得更好。”我的第二个回答是，这很混乱。在比赛开始之前，选择时间<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="t"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。问问琳达，她更喜欢哪种财富分配<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="t"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">方式</span></span></span></span></span></span>：她通过自己的策略获得的分配，还是洛根的策略分配的分配？她会回答，她的：它的预期财富为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" £1.2^t "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1.2</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.591em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">英镑</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.225em;"><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.3em; width: 0.5em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>洛根的预期财富仅为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" £1.04^t "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1.04</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.607em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">英镑</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.225em;"><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.3em; width: 0.5em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>并且，在未来的某个时候，在她破产后，询问琳达，根据她当时的了解，她是否认为她过去的决定是错误的。她会说不：她每一步都下了注，以最大化她的预期财富，其中一个与她背道而驰，但这就是生活。想想看，如果没有的话，她现在会有多少钱！ （下一个也没有，或者之后的一个……）值得冒这个险。</p><p>你可能会问“但是游戏结束后会发生什么？概率为 1，琳达没有钱，洛根有无限”。但之后就没有了！洛根永远不会停止。您可以将各种限制视为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" t→∞ "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">→</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∞</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，但限制并不总是表现良好<sup><a href="#fn:convergence" rel="footnote">2</a></sup> 。如果你在游戏中施加一些停止行为——固定的或概率的轮数限制——那么你会发现琳达的策略毫无争议地在游戏结束后给她比洛根更好的回报（根据琳达的说法），当她破产的概率为只是<em>非常接近</em>1。</p><p>或者，“但在某个时候，洛根将比琳达更富有！根据琳达的价值观，洛根将超过琳达的概率为 1。”是的，但是您将洛根在某个时间点的财富与琳达在更早的某个时间点的财富进行比较。当洛根的财富确实超过了她失去一切时所拥有的数额时，她可以安慰自己，因为她知道如果她<em>没有</em>失去一切，她现在就会<em>赚到钱</em>。她对此表示同意。</p><p>我想你在这里可以做的一件事就是假装你可以在有限的时间内进行无限轮的游戏。然后 Linda 需要做出选择：她可以在所有有限的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" n "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span>处最大化<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" t_n "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>处的预期财富，或者她可以在<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" t_ω "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ω</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>处最大化预期财富，即紧接在所有有限时间步之后的时间步。我们可以经常挥手说，让她自己下注会实现前者，让洛根下注会实现后者，尽管我不赞同我们在这里处理无限的方式。</p><p>即便如此，我认为我们所说的是琳达的具体情况不明确。假设她获得了一笔贷款，“我现在给你 1 英镑，你一周后给我 2 英镑”。她会接受吗？我可以想象一个接受的琳达和一个拒绝的琳达，两人仍然是期望金钱最大化者，只是在不同时间接受期望和/或扩大“金钱”以包括债务。所以你可以想象一个琳达为了长期收益而做出短期牺牲的预期金钱，并且（再次，比医生建议的更用力地挥舞你的手）你可以想象她接受了洛根的赌注。但这更多的是关于延迟满足，而不是洛根的效用函数对琳达来说比她自己的更好，或类似的东西。</p><p>我不确定我是否见过处理这个问题的实用函数处理？ （问题是“如果你的效用函数使得在时间<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="t_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>时最大化预期效用并不能在时间<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="t_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span>时</span></span></span></span></span>最大化预期效用怎么办？”）这对 Linda 来说并不比对 Logan 更重要，只是对 Logan 来说不太明显鉴于此设置。</p><p>所以我不同意琳达更喜欢洛根的效用函数。</p><h3>反击</h3><p>我的第三个回复是：如果你认为这对琳达来说很尴尬，那就看我让洛根也这么做。也许<em>不太</em>一样。我认为整体故事是一致的，但也有显着的差异。</p><p>我不能向洛根打赌，让他赌上自己的全部财产。任何可能的奖励都无法说服他接受哪怕一丁点钱用完的可能性。他不会冒着耗尽最后一分钱的风险来获得<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" £(3 ↑↑↑ 3) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.225em;"><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.3em; width: 0.5em;">英镑</span></span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.225em;"><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.314em;">↑↑↑↑↑</span> <span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.314em;">3</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">，</span></span></span></span></span></span>即使他输掉的机会<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 1 / (3 ↑↑↑↑ 3) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">是</span></span><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.225em;"><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.314em;">3</span> <span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.314em;">↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</span> <span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.314em;">3</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">3</span></span></span></span></span></span> <sup><a href="#fn:knuth" rel="footnote">。</a></sup></p><p>但我可以向他打赌，他会赌上<em>一切，只留下一分钱</em>。我可以将这个赌注的赔率定为 60/40，对他有利，就像琳达上面的赌注一样，或者任何其他有限的概率。如果他赢了，我可以以相同的赔率再给他一次赌注。还有一次，直到他最终输了，不能再下注了。就像琳达一样，他将能够预见到这一点，并且他会支持他的每一步行动。</p><p>我该怎么做呢？我不能简单地增加赌注的回报与赌注比率。如果投注返回您本金的几倍，并且获胜机会为 60%，则 Logan 的首选本金金额绝不会超过其资金的 60%。</p><p>但谁说我需要给他这个选择呢？ Logan 起价为 1 英镑，他的估价为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \ln(100) ≈ 4.6052 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">ln</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">100</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">≈</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">4.6052</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。 <sup><a href="#fn:zero-point" rel="footnote">4</a></sup>我可以向他提供一个赌注，他对我的 20.55 英镑下注 0.99 英镑，获胜机会为 60%。他看重赌注</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 0.4\ln(100 - 99) + 0.6\ln(100 + 2055) ≈ 4.6053 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.4</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">英寸</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">100</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">99</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.6</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">英寸</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">100</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2055</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">≈</span></spa